2. Detailed Roadmap (Task-Level)
Status values example: Not Started / In Progress / Blocked / Completed
Phase 1: Initiation & Planning
Task
Identify stakeholders (Platform, Cohesity, Security, Network, App teams)
Define scope & success criteria
Define supported OpenShift versions
Define supported Cohesity versions
Define in-scope backup/restore use cases
Risk assessment & dependency identification
Project plan & milestones sign-off
Phase 2: Design & Architecture
Task
High-level architecture diagram
Network connectivity design (firewalls, ports, routing)
Authentication model (RBAC, service accounts, secrets)
Namespace strategy for Cohesity components
ACM governance model
Backup/restore workflow design
Failure & recovery scenarios
Final design review & approval
Phase 3: POC in LLE
Task
Provision LLE OpenShift cluster
Verify connectivity to Cohesity on-prem
Install Cohesity components
Validate namespace isolation
Validate backup of sample workloads
Validate restore (same cluster)
Validate restore (new namespace)
POC success criteria validation
POC sign-off
Phase 4: Build & Automation
Task
Create Cohesity namespaces via ACM
Define ACM policies (RBAC, quotas, labels)
GitOps repo structure definition
Policy-as-code review
Secrets management integration
CI validation for policies
Phase 5: Testing & Validation
Task
Functional test cases definition
Backup/restore test matrix
Negative test cases (failure, corruption)
Performance tests (backup duration, restore SLA)
Scalability tests (multiple namespaces)
Security tests (RBAC, access isolation)
Disaster recovery simulation
Test results review & sign-off
Phase 6: Governance, Security & PTO
Task
Security architecture review
Compliance mapping (data residency, encryption)
PTO documentation preparation
Risk & exception handling
PTO approval
Phase 7: QA, UAT & RACI
Task
QA environment validation
UAT scenarios with sample apps
Business acceptance sign-off
RACI model definition
Ownership clarification (Day-2 ops)
Phase 8: Release Readiness
Task
Runbook creation
Monitoring & alerting integration
Backup SLA documentation
Rollback plan
Release readiness review
Phase 9: Production Release
Task
Production ACM policy deployment
Production Cohesity integration
Smoke testing
Production sign-off
Phase 10: Enablement & Adoption
Task
Internal team demo
Business user demos
User onboarding documentation
How-to guides (backup/restore)
FAQ & troubleshooting docs
Knowledge transfer to ops teams
Phase 11: Post-Release & Optimization
Task
Post-implementation review
Feedback collection
Performance tuning
Feature backlog creation
